For example, in my city
of Kampala, Uganda

23
00:01:17,634 --> 00:01:21,246
examples of our on-site
infrastructure include

24
00:01:21,425 --> 00:01:26,075
panned middle and high income areas
with good road infrastructure

25
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:29,731
which are mostly connected
by sewer or septic tanks

26
00:01:29,916 --> 00:01:32,716
with a low solid content.

27
00:01:33,112 --> 00:01:36,412
Unplanned densely populated
low-income areas

28
00:01:36,611 --> 00:01:40,048
with poor accessibility
in fecal sludge from pit latrines

29
00:01:40,229 --> 00:01:42,941
has got a very high solid content

30
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:47,707
and peri-urban areas with
