In this module, we have learned that
a number of different collection

122
00:07:33,836 --> 00:07:37,248
and transport technologies
are used in urban areas 

123
00:07:37,589 --> 00:07:42,064
corresponding to different physical
and socio-economic realities.

124
00:07:43,597 --> 00:07:45,535
In addition, a number of different

125
00:07:45,709 --> 00:07:47,197
collection and transport
technologies

126
00:07:47,375 --> 00:07:52,375
were introduced that are appropriate
